data.description: Welcome to this magnificent home, the exterior seamlessly blends stone and stucco, crafting an entrance that is both elegant and inviting. As you step inside, you will be invited by  views of Pine Valley, Snow Canyon, and the surrounding areas, inviting you to bask in the harmonious blend of tranquility and comfort. A private casita provides a serene retreat for guests, while the expansive main living area, adorned with large picture windows and a walkout deck, sets the stage for breathtaking moments.Descend to the elegant walkout basement, featuring a second kitchen, three guest bedrooms, family room, and game room. This space provides a separate realm for both fun and relaxation, enhancing the overall allure of the home. Absolutely no detail has been left to chance in this beautifully designed, decorated, and built residence. Once you come, you will want to stay, captivated by the thoughtful craftsmanship and inviting ambiance.
